== {{ill|Hyōtan-yama Kofun|ja|瓢箪山古墳}} == * {{ill|Komaka Hyōtan-yama Kofun|ja|駒岡瓢箪山古墳}} - Located in **Tsurumi Ward, Yokohama City, Kanagawa Prefecture**, part of the **Komaka Kofun Cluster**. * {{ill|Hyōtan-yama Kofun (Kannami Town)|ja|瓢箪山古墳 (函南町)}} - Located in **Kannami Town, Tagata District, Shizuoka Prefecture**. * {{ill|Moriyama Hyōtan-yama Kofun|ja|守山瓢箪山古墳}} - Located in **Moriyama Ward, Nagoya City, Aichi Prefecture**. * {{ill|Azuchi Hyōtan-yama Kofun|ja|安土瓢箪山古墳}} - Located in **Ōmihachiman City, Shiga Prefecture**. * {{ill|Hyōtan-yama Kofun (Higashi-Osaka City)|ja|瓢箪山古墳 (東大阪市)}} - Located in **Higashi-Osaka City, Osaka Prefecture**, part of the **Yamahata Kofun Cluster**. * {{ill|Saki Hyōtan-yama Kofun|ja|佐紀瓢箪山古墳}} - Located in **Nara City, Nara Prefecture**, part of the **Saki Tatenami Kofun Cluster**.
== {{ill|Hyōtan-zuka Kofun|ja|瓢箪塚古墳}} == * {{ill|Hyōtan-zuka Kofun (Mooka City)|ja|瓢箪塚古墳 (真岡市)}} - Located in **Mooka City, Tochigi Prefecture**. * {{ill|Komori Hyōtan-zuka Kofun|ja|小森瓢箪塚古墳}} - Located in **Shiroi City, Chiba Prefecture**{{sfn|Takahana|2005}}. * {{ill|Yamasaki Hyōtan-zuka Kofun|ja|山崎ひょうたん塚古墳}} - Located in **Sakura City, Chiba Prefecture**. * {{ill|Hyōtan-zuka Kofun (Ebina City)|ja|瓢箪塚古墳 (海老名市)}} - Located in **Ebina City, Kanagawa Prefecture**, part of the **Kamihamada Kofun Cluster**. * {{ill|Hyōtan-zuka (Kobirasawa Kofun)|ja|小平沢古墳}} - Located in **Kōfu City, Yamanashi Prefecture**, an alternate name for **Kobirasawa Kofun**. * {{ill|Hyōtan-zuka Kofun (Shizuoka City)|ja|瓢箪塚古墳 (静岡市)}} - Located in **Shimizu Ward, Shizuoka City, Shizuoka Prefecture**, part of the **Nishinohara Kofun Cluster**.
== Other Kofun == * {{ill|Hyōzuka Kofun (Kakegawa City)|ja|瓢塚古墳 (掛川市)}} - Located in **Kakegawa City, Shizuoka Prefecture**. * {{ill|Shiramizu Hyōzuka Kofun|ja|白水瓢塚古墳}} - Located in **Kobe City, Hyogo Prefecture**. * {{ill|Yoro Hyōzuka Kofun|ja|丁瓢塚古墳}} - Located in **Himeji City, Hyogo Prefecture**, part of the **Yoro Kofun Cluster**. * {{ill|Hisago-yama Kofun|ja|瓢山古墳}} - Located in **Shōbara City, Hiroshima Prefecture**. * {{ill|Hisago-zuka Kofun (Kannonji City)|ja|ひさご塚古墳 (観音寺市)}} - Located in **Kannonji City, Kagawa Prefecture**. * {{ill|Hyōzuka Kofun (Karatsu City)|ja|瓢塚古墳 (唐津市)}} - Located in **Karatsu City, Saga Prefecture**. * {{ill|Hisago-zuka Kofun|ja|ひさご塚古墳}} - Located in **Higashisonogi Town, Higashisonogi District, Nagasaki Prefecture**.
