{{afc comment|Wikidata entry (none) Wikidata name: (none) [[User:Immanuelle|Immanuelle]] ([[User talk:Immanuelle|talk]]) 07:51, 11 June 2025 (UTC)}} '''List of Kofun in the Japanese Archipelago with the Name "Hyō"''' (「瓢」の付く日本列島の古墳一覧)
This article provides a list of kofun (ancient Kofuns) and kofun clusters in the '''Japanese Archipelago''' whose names include '''"Hyō"''' (瓢 / ひさご), which refers to a '''gourd'''.
== Overview == Throughout '''Japan''', there are many kofun with names like '''"Hyōtan-zuka"''' (瓢箪塚 / ひょうたんづか, ひさごづか) and '''"Hyōtan-yama"''' (瓢箪山 / ひょうたんやま, ひさごやま). In addition, there are variations such as '''"Hyō-zuka"''' (瓢塚 / ひょうづか, ひさごづか), '''"Hisago-zuka"''', and '''"Hisago-yama"''', as well as names where '''"Hyō"''' is written in '''hiragana'''. These names are believed to originate from the resemblance of '''keyhole-shaped kofun''' ('''zenpō-kōen-fun''') or '''square-fronted kofun''' ('''zenpō-kōhō-fun''') to a '''gourd (瓢箪, hisago / hyōtan)''' when viewed from the side.
== {{ill|Hyōtan-yama Kofun|ja|瓢箪山古墳|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hyōtan-yama Kofun|qq=}} == * {{ill|Komaka Hyōtan-yama Kofun|ja|駒岡瓢箪山古墳|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Komaka Hyōtan-yama Kofun|qq=}} - Located in '''Tsurumi Ward, Yokohama City, Kanagawa Prefecture''', part of the '''Komaka Kofun Cluster'''. * {{ill|Hyōtan-yama Kofun (Kannami Town)|ja|瓢箪山古墳 (函南町)|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hyōtan-yama Kofun (Kannami Town)|qq=}} - Located in '''Kannami Town, Tagata District, Shizuoka Prefecture'''. * {{ill|Moriyama Hyōtan-yama Kofun|ja|守山瓢箪山古墳|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Moriyama Hyōtan-yama Kofun|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} - Located in '''Moriyama Ward, Nagoya City, Aichi Prefecture'''. * [[:en:Azuchi-Hyōtanyama Kofun|Azuchi Hyōtan-yama Kofun]] - Located in '''Ōmihachiman City, Shiga Prefecture'''. * {{ill|Hyōtan-yama Kofun (Higashi-Osaka City)|ja|瓢箪山古墳 (東大阪市)|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hyōtan-yama Kofun (Higashi-Osaka City)|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} - Located in '''Higashi-Osaka City, Osaka Prefecture''', part of the '''Yamahata Kofun Cluster'''. * [[:en:Saki Hyōtanyama Kofun|Saki Hyōtan-yama Kofun]] - Located in '''Nara City, Nara Prefecture''', part of the '''Saki Tatenami Kofun Cluster'''.
